<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Fragment from the upper part of the front of a garland <rs type="objectType">sarcophagus</rs> (for measurements see Isik 198)</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Inscribed along the upper rim, possibly also on the central tabella.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p> Quite well designed and cut, with what appear to be intentionally uneven heights (recalling no. <xref type="inscription" n="1522" href="150341">15.341</xref>); ω for omega.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date cert="low" notAfter="0275" notBefore="0225"> Perhaps middle third century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>, <rs type="criteria">decoration</rs>)
</p>
</div>
